+# JavaScriptDialogHandlerDetails Object
+
+* `frame` [WebFrameMain](../web-frame-main.md) - The frame that requested the
+  JavaScript dialog.
+* `type` string - The dialog type. Can be `alert`, `confirm`, `prompt`, or
+  `beforeunload`.
+* `messageText` string - The dialog message text.
+* `defaultPromptText` string - The default text for `prompt` dialogs. Empty for
+  other dialog types.
+* `url` string - The last committed URL of the frame that requested the dialog.
+* `isMainFrame` boolean - Whether the frame that requested the dialog is the
+  main frame.
+* `isReload` boolean (optional) - Whether the `beforeunload` dialog was
+  triggered by a reload.
